&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Abstract&lt;br /&gt;The fuzzy-interpolative systems are a Soft Computing item, hybridizing&amp;nbsp;Sugeno&amp;nbsp;fuzzy systems with linear interpolation networks (look-up-tables). They share the fuzzy linguistic knowledge&amp;nbsp;representation&amp;nbsp;with the matrix/memory structures&amp;rsquo; extreme applicative efficiency.&amp;nbsp;Neuro-fuzzy applications are derived very conveniently.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Some basic self-adaptive techniques are presented: gradual PD-PID shifting, self-adaptation by&amp;nbsp; linguistic phase trajectory analysis, fuzzy-fusion correctors and LUT planners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Applications from several fields of activity are briefly presented: adaptive control, traffic&amp;nbsp;management, renewable energy management, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Brief Bio:&amp;nbsp;Marius M.&amp;nbsp;Balas, IEEE Senior Member, is currently a Full Professor at the University &amp;ldquo;Aurel&amp;nbsp;Vlaicu&amp;rdquo; of Arad (Romania). He is the author of 4 books, 14 book chapters, 83 indexed articles, 40 papers in other journals and conference proceedings and 7 invention patents. His research interests are in Electronic Circuits,&amp;nbsp;Modeling&amp;nbsp;and Simulation, Adaptive Control, Intelligent and Fuzzy Systems, Greenhouses and Intelligent Transportation. The main original concepts introduced by&amp;nbsp;Prof.&amp;nbsp;Marius M.&amp;nbsp;Balas&amp;nbsp;are: the fuzzy-interpolative systems, the passive greenhouse, the intelligent roof-top greenhouse, the constant time to collision optimization of the traffic, the imposed distance braking, the internal model bronze casting, PWM inverters for railway coaches, the rejection of the switching controllers effect by phase trajectory analysis, etc. He has been mentor for student research challenges, awarded by Microsoft Imagine Cup, GDF Suez,&amp;nbsp;etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
